=== Research Opportunities

Areas where respiratory and allergy medicine expertise could advance ME/CFS understanding:
    - *Ventilation-perfusion mismatch mechanisms*: Indirect evidence exists from elevated VE/VCO2 ratios; direct V/Q scanning studies are lacking
    - *Respiratory muscle function*: Objective diaphragm function assessment in patients reporting respiratory muscle fatigue
    - *MCAS prevalence in general populations*: Establishing baseline rates in allergy practice for comparison to ME/CFS cohorts
    - *Breathing pattern disorder interventions*: Capnometry-guided retraining protocols adapted for ME/CFS energy limitations


